  "title": "Operating Theatre Nurses, 5 Days Office Hours, ( $34 per hour ) #HVY",
  "description": "<p><u><strong>Key Responsibilities</strong></u></p><ul><li>Perform orthopedic procedures within scope of practice and facility privileges</li></ul><ul><li>Collaborate with multidisciplinary healthcare teams to optimize patient outcomes</li></ul><ul><li>Maintain accurate and timely medical records</li></ul><ul><li>Ensure compliance with healthcare regulations, safety standards, and professional guidelines</li></ul><ul><li>Participate in quality improvement, continuing education, and clinical governance activities</li></ul><p></p><p><u><strong>Qualifications and Requirements</strong></u></p><p></p><ul><li>Registered with Singapore Nursing Board</li><li>Min 3 years Experience as Staff Nurse in operating theatre</li></ul><p></p><p>Interested candidates please send in your resume to:</p><p></p><p><u><strong>valerie@recruitexpress.com.sg</strong></u></p><p></p><p>EA Personnel: Valerie Yong Kian Fung</p><p>CEI No.: R1103704</p><p>Recruit Express Pte Ltd, EA License No.: 99C4599</p>",
